Info.Writer: Matt Lieberman (screenplay by), Charles Addams (based on characters created by), Conrad Vernon (story by), Pamela Pettler (screenplay), Matt Lieberman (story), Erica Rivinoja (story by)

Info.Plot: The eccentrically macabre family moves to a bland suburb where Wednesday Addams' friendship with the daughter of a hostile and conformist local reality show host exacerbates conflict between the families.
